  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/0b99004c3345c5c4ff026baad734f37c.poster.avif?t=1747241878\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/0b99004c3345c5c4ff026baad734f37c.webm?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/0b99004c3345c5c4ff026baad734f37c.mp4?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Trapped in Darkness</strong><br>You find yourself lost in a dense, eerie forest during a heavy rainstorm. In the distance, you see the light of an old, secluded house. Seeking shelter from the storm, you step inside, but quickly realize it’s a trap. A demonic entity has imprisoned you within the house, and the only way forward is through a series of rooms filled with dark secrets and intricate puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/7bcd355b3b3c59fd2feddd3592580b6f.poster.avif?t=1747241878\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/7bcd355b3b3c59fd2feddd3592580b6f.webm?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/7bcd355b3b3c59fd2feddd3592580b6f.mp4?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Race Against Time</strong><br>You have a limited amount of time to solve the puzzles in each room. When all three candles extinguish, death awaits you. This is a test of speed and endurance, where every minute could be crucial.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/378733dac3e5ab9c3525378dfb2ecacd.poster.avif?t=1747241878\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/378733dac3e5ab9c3525378dfb2ecacd.webm?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/378733dac3e5ab9c3525378dfb2ecacd.mp4?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combination of Horror and Escape Room Mechanics</strong><br>Each room contains its unique puzzles that gradually reveal the chilling story of the demonic entity holding you captive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/4910d9b7eb0617fb2429c8070a89e1fe.poster.avif?t=1747241878\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/4910d9b7eb0617fb2429c8070a89e1fe.webm?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/4910d9b7eb0617fb2429c8070a89e1fe.mp4?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/148f20efaa4b9526ef98137601d3fb8c.poster.avif?t=1747241878\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/148f20efaa4b9526ef98137601d3fb8c.webm?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/148f20efaa4b9526ef98137601d3fb8c.mp4?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atmospheric Thriller:</strong> Immerse yourself in a haunting house where every step is filled with tension and a sense of constant danger. The darkness envelops you, and the demonic entity relentlessly attempts to terrify you, creating uncertainty with every move you make.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Timed Puzzles:</strong> Solve unique puzzles in the rooms while racing against the clock — when the candles go out, death awaits.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Escape Room-Style Progression:</strong> Navigate a series of rooms, each with its atmosphere, challenges, and fears, as you move closer to freedom.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chilling Narrative:</strong> Piece together clues and uncover the story of the demonic force that seeks to keep you in this sinister place.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This horror-puzzle game will test your endurance and wit — will you be able to escape the trap before darkness claims you forever?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/0b99004c3345c5c4ff026baad734f37c.poster.avif?t=1747241878\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/0b99004c3345c5c4ff026baad734f37c.webm?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/0b99004c3345c5c4ff026baad734f37c.mp4?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Trapped in Darkness</strong><br>You find yourself lost in a dense, eerie forest during a heavy rainstorm. In the distance, you see the light of an old, secluded house. Seeking shelter from the storm, you step inside, but quickly realize it’s a trap. A demonic entity has imprisoned you within the house, and the only way forward is through a series of rooms filled with dark secrets and intricate puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/7bcd355b3b3c59fd2feddd3592580b6f.poster.avif?t=1747241878\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/7bcd355b3b3c59fd2feddd3592580b6f.webm?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/7bcd355b3b3c59fd2feddd3592580b6f.mp4?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Race Against Time</strong><br>You have a limited amount of time to solve the puzzles in each room. When all three candles extinguish, death awaits you. This is a test of speed and endurance, where every minute could be crucial.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/378733dac3e5ab9c3525378dfb2ecacd.poster.avif?t=1747241878\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/378733dac3e5ab9c3525378dfb2ecacd.webm?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/378733dac3e5ab9c3525378dfb2ecacd.mp4?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combination of Horror and Escape Room Mechanics</strong><br>Each room contains its unique puzzles that gradually reveal the chilling story of the demonic entity holding you captive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/4910d9b7eb0617fb2429c8070a89e1fe.poster.avif?t=1747241878\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/4910d9b7eb0617fb2429c8070a89e1fe.webm?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/4910d9b7eb0617fb2429c8070a89e1fe.mp4?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/148f20efaa4b9526ef98137601d3fb8c.poster.avif?t=1747241878\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/148f20efaa4b9526ef98137601d3fb8c.webm?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332550/extras/148f20efaa4b9526ef98137601d3fb8c.mp4?t=1747241878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atmospheric Thriller:</strong> Immerse yourself in a haunting house where every step is filled with tension and a sense of constant danger. The darkness envelops you, and the demonic entity relentlessly attempts to terrify you, creating uncertainty with every move you make.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Timed Puzzles:</strong> Solve unique puzzles in the rooms while racing against the clock — when the candles go out, death awaits.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Escape Room-Style Progression:</strong> Navigate a series of rooms, each with its atmosphere, challenges, and fears, as you move closer to freedom.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chilling Narrative:</strong> Piece together clues and uncover the story of the demonic force that seeks to keep you in this sinister place.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This horror-puzzle game will test your endurance and wit — will you be able to escape the trap before darkness claims you forever?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
